show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/s7d2gW
show.description: A husband finds himself trapped in a madman’s twisted game, forced to endure a nightmarish journey while his family remains helpless in a cargo trailer. As the deranged abductor drives through the night, he recounts three horrifying tales, each more disturbing than the last. With time running out, the husband must find a way to escape before he becomes the final chapter in this terrifying saga.
